- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as modal logic is used in AI for reasoning about knowledge and belief. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as modal logic has been used in some machine learning applications. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as modal logic has been used in the specification and verification of programming languages. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as modal logic has been used in some algorithmic applications.
